124
00:06:29,540 --> 00:06:30,870
do you think

125
00:06:31,080 --> 00:06:32,500
it makes sense as well?

126
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:34,480
Of course not.

127
00:06:36,300 --> 00:06:37,430
I could have

128
00:06:37,860 --> 00:06:39,600
put her in her place

129
00:06:39,930 --> 00:06:41,280
