132
00:06:49,610 --> 00:06:50,330
Mo Yan.

133
00:06:50,920 --> 00:06:52,320
What are you talking about?

134
00:06:53,340 --> 00:06:54,980
Even though I don't think of her as a mother,

135
00:06:55,720 --> 00:06:57,340
