138
00:07:02,060 --> 00:07:02,790
From now on,

139
00:07:03,150 --> 00:07:04,500
I will take back my respect.

140
00:07:05,010 --> 00:07:06,850
If she crosses the line again,

141
00:07:07,250 --> 00:07:08,270
I will not tolerate her.

142
00:07:08,770 --> 00:07:10,110
How dare you!

143
00:07:10,770 --> 00:07:11,560
Get out!

144
00:07:12,030 --> 00:07:13,830
Go to your mother's Xiao Xuan Village!

145
00:07:26,270 --> 00:07:27,000
Yan.

146
00:07:27,090 --> 00:07:29,050
You've really pissed First Uncle off.

147
00:07:29,150 --> 00:07:31,230
I heard his voice cracked outside.

148
00:07:33,440 --> 00:07:34,990
I was polite enough.

149
00:07:35,800 --> 00:07:38,090
Lady Liu is getting more arrogant

150
00:07:38,170 --> 00:07:39,380
