161
00:07:57,430 --> 00:07:59,270
Everyone knows what Lady Liu

162
00:07:59,590 --> 00:08:00,660
is trying to do

163
00:08:00,680 --> 00:08:02,080
except my father.

164
00:08:03,790 --> 00:08:05,730
The mansion is always in turmoil.

165
00:08:05,980 --> 00:08:06,550
I think

166
00:08:06,910 --> 00:08:08,350
my father and Lady Liu

167
00:08:08,390 --> 00:08:09,420
deserve all the credit.

168
00:08:10,770 --> 00:08:12,580
Now, Young Madam joined the battle

169
00:08:12,720 --> 00:08:14,690
and fought with Lady Liu

170
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:15,780
neck and neck.

171
00:08:15,930 --> 00:08:16,800
To be honest,

172
00:08:16,910 --> 00:08:18,270
