173
00:08:22,380 --> 00:08:23,010
Brother.

174
00:08:23,430 --> 00:08:24,160
Yan.

175
00:08:32,559 --> 00:08:34,350
You're so arrogant

176
00:08:34,600 --> 00:08:35,590
