177
00:08:36,760 --> 00:08:38,200
You still have time to scold him?

178
00:08:38,440 --> 00:08:40,020
Your father will teach you a lesson later.

179
00:08:42,320 --> 00:08:43,299
Hurry up.

180
00:08:53,630 --> 00:08:54,920
Let's depart tomorrow.

181
00:08:55,220 --> 00:08:56,810
Tell Mo Yu to pack some things.

182
00:08:58,470 --> 00:08:59,240
Yan.

183
00:09:00,210 --> 00:09:02,180
Are you sure you can find out her identity

184
00:09:02,370 --> 00:09:03,890
