185
00:09:04,090 --> 00:09:05,770
If she is related to that demon,

186
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:07,510
her connection with the fragments

187
00:09:07,660 --> 00:09:08,730
will be more than that.

188
00:09:09,810 --> 00:09:11,480
After hearing what Wolf King said,

189
00:09:11,830 --> 00:09:12,910
I suspected

190
00:09:13,070 --> 00:09:13,910
the fragments were

191
00:09:13,950 --> 00:09:14,810
more than two pieces.

192
00:09:15,580 --> 00:09:16,220
That's right.

193
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:19,300
I've also been investigating this matter lately.

194
00:09:19,740 --> 00:09:21,130
It seems that many demons

195
00:09:21,700 --> 00:09:22,890
are looking for the fragments.

196
00:09:24,520 --> 00:09:26,340
Xiao Xuan Village is located at Mount Niuyang.

197
00:09:26,710 --> 00:09:28,790
It's one of the origins of the demon clan.

198
00:09:29,350 --> 00:09:31,030
Recently, the demons have been acting abnormally.

199
00:09:31,460 --> 00:09:33,090
We should look into it, no matter what.

200
00:09:34,030 --> 00:09:35,020
Maybe

201
00:09:35,050 --> 00:09:35,820
we may discover something new.

202
00:09:46,330 --> 00:09:47,520
What are you worried about?

203
00:09:50,590 --> 00:09:51,110
Nothing.

204
00:09:57,370 --> 00:09:58,280
Yan.

205
00:09:58,820 --> 00:10:00,270
You can be softhearted,

206
00:10:00,440 --> 00:10:01,050
but I

207
00:10:01,470 --> 00:10:02,670
