246
00:12:09,880 --> 00:12:10,920
I have no choice either.

247
00:12:11,550 --> 00:12:12,500
What do you mean?

248
00:12:14,110 --> 00:12:16,360
Every time I was in danger,

249
00:12:16,930 --> 00:12:19,040
you would be the first to save me.

250
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:22,780
I was just passing by.

251
00:12:23,920 --> 00:12:25,340
So I regret it.

252
00:12:25,370 --> 00:12:26,820
I take back what I said.

253
00:12:26,950 --> 00:12:28,390
Don't disbelieve me,

254
00:12:28,420 --> 00:12:30,000
and don't ignore me, okay?

255
00:12:40,510 --> 00:12:41,970
