267
00:13:11,910 --> 00:13:13,670
Yesterday, I heard

268
00:13:14,740 --> 00:13:15,850
what you said clearly

269
00:13:16,810 --> 00:13:18,490
when I sent you back to the room.

270
00:13:18,550 --> 00:13:19,160
Then...

271
00:13:20,570 --> 00:13:22,270
Tell me that

272
00:13:22,580 --> 00:13:24,290
you married me,

273
00:13:24,760 --> 00:13:26,410
not anyone else.

274
00:13:33,800 --> 00:13:35,220
But I have to know

275
00:13:36,140 --> 00:13:38,000
whom I married.

276
00:13:42,370 --> 00:13:44,370
