282
00:14:07,550 --> 00:14:08,910
Pack up first.

283
00:14:09,400 --> 00:14:10,030
Tomorrow,

284
00:14:10,420 --> 00:14:12,600
I'll take you to a villa to recuperate for a while.

285
00:14:13,360 --> 00:14:14,670
