286
00:14:14,960 --> 00:14:16,440
It would be very helpful for your cultivation.

287
00:14:17,090 --> 00:14:17,980
Really?

288
00:14:18,010 --> 00:14:18,830
No.

289
00:14:21,520 --> 00:14:22,330
Just kidding.

290
00:14:29,130 --> 00:14:30,600
Thank you, Mo Yan.

